game.name: Baby Emma Bridesmaid Outfits
game.description:
Baby Emma looks very happy since this pretty girl has got the invitation from the wedding of her close friend. She is going to play the role of a wedding flower girl on the special day of the marriage of her closed one. Everything is good, except the preparation of outfit for the girl. Will you give your helping hands to this needy baby princess? Join Baby Emma Bridesmaid Outfits and be prepared to guide her decide a perfect combination of clothes! 

This cute and little girl is very positive about your outfit choice. Go through her wider and exclusive collection of clothes and accessories and choose the ones that make her look shine on that day in this brand new dressing game for girls! Give a beautiful golden color crown to her head or choose a lovely dark purple color hat for the lady! Find a short hairstyle or shine her look with a long hairstyle! Select a blue color top and match it with a black color short skirt in this html5 princess dress up game!

Dress her up with a purple and grey color frock or choose an orange color dress for this cute baby!  Do not forget to complete her look with a lovely pair of matching shoes or sandals. Change the outfit and accessory options by clicking the left and right click given at the top of her wardrobe! Good luck to help her pick up the awesome clothes for an excellent work!! You can browse through our wide array of girls games that are playable on multiple devices without download. Come and have a fun!!
